# --- Knowledge-OS Framework .gitignore ---
# Use when exporting __Framework to a (separate, OUTSIDE-OneDrive) git repo.

# Installed dependencies — run `npm install` in tooling/ per bootstrap/RUN.md
node_modules/
**/node_modules/

# Regenerable tool validation scratch / sandbox outputs
tooling/_validation/
migration/_validation/
slices/focus-detector/graph-index.snapshot.json
slices/focus-detector/focus_signals*.json
slices/focus-detector/person_profile.detected.json
**/*.tmp
**/*.drift-fix.tmp

# Instance-Zero (reference-instance) scratch / gap analysis — keep private, do not ship
instance-zero/

# OS / editor noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ── COMPANY-SPECIFIC SEED ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# manifest.mot.json + company-seed.json contain MetaOptics-specific data
# (people names/emails, customer/project names, the context registry with
# real account names) — the reference instance ("Instance Zero"). They ship
# ONLY the generic mechanism (templates + tools + docs + the *.example.json
# synthetic instance), never the filled MOT instance:
tooling/manifest.mot.json
tooling/company-seed.json
GENERALIZATION_AUDIT.md
